data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own a 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bath, 2 car garage home in a very desirable Community of Entrada in Cape Coral! Kitchen is complete with modern appliances, farmhouse sink, island and plenty of counter space - making cooking and entertaining a breeze with the open floor plan. Enjoy the Lake view and landscaped backyard  from the screened in lanai, with plenty of space to add a pool. Upgraded light fixtures and NEW ROOF 2023. Entrada offers their residents a state of the art amenity center; clubhouse, fitness center, resort style pool with a lap lane, splash pad, kids playground area, tennis and pickleball courts!! No Flood insurance required! Low HOA fees, and on City Water and Sewer. Entrada is minutes from local area shopping, golf, schools, hospitals and downtown Fort Myers. A must see!
